            <h2 class="iwra-postheader">
             <a class="PostHeader" href="/index.php/how-to-help">
              How to Help?
             </a>
            </h2>
            <div class="iwra-postcontent">
             <div class="iwra-article">
              <p class="visited">
               <strong>
                LOOKING FOR FUND TO EDUCATION:
               </strong>
              </p>
              <p style="text-align: justify;">
               The most essential factor for all round development of a child is “Love and security of a family”.Observing this fact deep in mind Padam lama established the first Vision Nepal Project in 2013.brings up Destitute children in a family like environment. It provides necessary education and training to help them integrate into the society as self reliant and useful citizens.The Idea of Vision Nepal project was accepted and supported by many people in the world and due to support from many friends,supporters and sponsors it spread throughout the world.Vision Nepal project is an independent,non-governmental social development organization. Generous support from all interested donors is the umbrella for the Vision Nepal Project.To become a donor member all you need to do is fill in and tick the relevant part below and send the same to us at YES ! I would like to help make a child’s dreams come true.
               <br />
               <br />
               <strong>
                I WOULD LIKE TO:
               </strong>
               <br />
               1) sponsor a child by contributing-$40/ per month.
               <br />
               2) Become a Vision Nepal Project member by contributing-$200/per year.
               <br />
               3) Become a life member of Vision Nepal Project by contributing-$500/After your willingness to donate for the educational fund for the children.
               <br />
               <br />
               <strong class="visited">
                HOW I CAN SEND TO MONEY &amp; BANK DETAILS ARE BELOW:
               </strong>
               <br />
               Bank of Kathmandu Ltd,
               <br />
               Kathmandu,Nepal
               <br />
               Swift Code : BOKLNPKA
               <br />
               Beneficiary :PEMA TSHERING LAMA.
               <br />
               A/C No. : 02-02-0000000-1 NPR
               <br />
               Bank of Kathmandu Ltd.
               <br />
               New Road branch.
              </p>
              <p>
               You may also help us by sending this appeal to your friends/ relatives/firms/and the interested parties who are eager to help the destitute child in Nepal and We have been told that it needs four to five days for the money to get into our account after you wire the same.above given is the detail of the bank.We hope either of them will come of help to you.Once again we thank you very much for your generous help to us:This is our Cell No +977-9843081190/9841321588
               <br />
               E-mail address:
